plc.examples

Class AccountTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • plc.examples.AccountTests

  • public class AccountTests
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains JUnit tests for Account. Test structure for steps 1 & 2 are provided, you must create this yourself for step 3. To run tests, either click the run icon on the left margin, which can be used to run all tests or only a specific test. You should make sure your tests are run through IntelliJ (File > Settings > Build, Execution, Deployment > Build Tools > Gradle > Run tests using IntelliJ IDEA). This ensures the name and inputs for the tests are displayed correctly in the run window.
